{"tid":172284,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A]台版MHRX(1) 有冇巴打玩緊？","createTime":"2017-03-25T20:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T19:47:58.000Z","uid":74386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c8fd412a2403663ddf579cfe17d77c059000c67","tid":172284,"uid":74386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T20:22:03.000Z","msg":"隻game咁好玩都無巴打玩緊？<br />\n就出16人強化版有冇人一齊屠龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：我都係想開個post出黎比玩緊嘅巴打有個約戰同吹水嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4819ece28de188532877120aa9aac9f81d8da2cd","tid":172284,"uid":4500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T20:25:31.000Z","msg":"介紹下"},{"pid":"0506f076a2b33ba43a3a4016ce8f531eedfdfe04","tid":172284,"uid":74386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T21:06:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>介紹下</blockquote><br />\n你想知啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果係點玩同介面係點比片你睇方便啲<br />\n同埋下面段片隻豪火龍係新出嘅怪 可以刷到5星裝<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fWzm3LAC-yY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfWzm3LAC-yY&d=KYS9j8ljDCWJrVyje8%2BOjQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=884ffc43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fWzm3LAC-yY</a><br />\n<br />\n同埋隻game啲裝極大部分都係可以打出黎<br />\n得好少部分係要抽<br />\n所以0課金都可以玩到好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就好似隻豪火龍咁係暫時最勁嘅裝備<br />\n啲石最主要係用黎買自動打怪,擴建裝備倉庫同開完場獎勵"},{"pid":"3fad8927b67be100cf9fcc5c5304d8fd564894f7","tid":172284,"uid":66965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T21:08:27.000Z","msg":"其實點解唔玩日版啊<br />\n日版嗰啲好玩好多<br />\n進度又快咁多<br />\n台版真係慢到嘔屎<br />\n又冇得抽裝<br />\n雖然其實隻game係幾好玩嘅"},{"pid":"241b8fab315cf61b1ebdbd8cf4dd499073468a87","tid":172284,"uid":74386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T21:22:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實點解唔玩日版啊<br />\n日版嗰啲好玩好多<